  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}{f 4 23 0 7 2 25 25}Are you scared?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 5 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 5 25 25}What a peculiar question.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 5 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 5 25 25}You must be a stranger to death if you think it is something to fear...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 8 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}{f 4 23 0 7 8 25 25}...What do you mean?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 1 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}You fear it because you do not understand it.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 5 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 5 25 25}I've lived long enough. I have nothing more to say.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 6 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 4 23 0 5 6 25 25}We have no interest in taking the life of someone who can't even move.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}{f 4 23 0 5 0 25 25}You will live to see if what you wished for comes true or not.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 9 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 4 23 0 3 9 25 25}Yeah, stay right there and think about what you've done.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 1 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}Hmph... What a truly baffling group you are...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}{f 4 23 0 5 0 25 25}We're finally here.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}{f 4 23 0 5 0 25 25}Up ahead is the summit of Tartarus.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}{f 4 23 0 5 0 25 25}...The Promised Place Ryoji mentioned.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
